2. Interpretation
In this Act, unless the context otherwise requires—
"Board" means the Board of the Botswana Savings Bank established under the Botswana Savings Bank Act (Cap. 56:03);
"Botswana Savings Bank" means the Botswana Savings Bank established under the Botswana Savings Bank Act;
"Company" means Botswana Savings Bank Limited, as continued under section 3;
